
-each class gets its own logger
-in main:
	want to tell logger that want to change the log level to log 
	everything of the logger and above
		-the default level is INFO
		-put package name in the logger parameter
		-create a handler to log it to anywhere you specify
			ConsoleHandler - print to console
			FileHandler, 

different levels of logging

SEVERE -
	- exception thrown and will ruin app
	
WARNING - 
	- something you should pay attention to but won't necessarily ruin app
	
INFO - 
	- message of events of app
	
CONFIG - 
	- want to make sure that app is configured properly
	
FINE, FINER, FINEST - use for debugging
